From: Alexey <alexey@karanyuk.com>
Date: Thu, 9 Apr 2026 14:50:03 +0300
Subject: [PATCH] Fix Hugo build: remove .Inner from formula shortcode, clean
 up repo

- Formula shortcode was using .Inner but called without closing tags,
  causing Hugo build failure on GitHub Actions
- Removed .Inner from shortcode template (all data passed via params)
- Removed all {{< /formula >}} closing tags from content
- Replaced peaceiris/actions-hugo (deprecated Node.js 20) with direct
  Hugo .deb install in workflow
- Added proper .gitignore (public/, .DS_Store, etc.)
- Removed accidentally committed public/ build artifacts
- Added new content and theme updates

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>
